text: It’s almost eerie to see normal life in Sweden. Yes, they have more #Coronavirus cases than other Scandinavian countries. But not more, proportionately, than many other countries that have gone into lockdown. And unlike the rest of the world, Sweden still has an economy! https://t.co/bvIRgdjaG0
